《'''蒙馬儒的日落'''》是[[荷蘭|荷蘭]][[後印象派|後印象派]]畫家[[文森·梵谷|文森·梵谷]]創作於1888年7月的一幅[[油畫|油畫]]<ref name="BBC">{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-24014186 |title=New Vincent Van Gogh painting identified |access-date=2013-09-11 |archive-date=2015-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150929062111/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-24014186 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="AFP1">[http://www.afp.com/en/news/topstories/long-lost-van-gogh-painting-unveiled-amsterdam Long-lost Van Gogh painting unveiled in Amsterdam] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130911233449/http://www.afp.com/en/news/topstories/long-lost-van-gogh-painting-unveiled-amsterdam |date=2013-09-11 }}</ref>。它描繪的是[[法國|法國]][[普羅旺斯|普羅旺斯]][[蒙馬儒修道院|蒙馬儒修道院]]遺址（見于此畫背景）附近山丘的景色<ref name="BBC" /><ref name="Guardian">{{Cite web |url=http://www.theguardian.com/artanddesign/2013/sep/09/van-gogh-painting-discovered |title=Newly discovered Van Gogh painting kept in attic for years |access-date=2013-09-11 |archive-date=2020-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130212752/https://www.theguardian.com/artanddesign/2013/sep/09/van-gogh-painting-discovered |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2013年前，這畫的真偽並未能得到確定，直至同年9月，它才得到專家的肯定<ref name="BBC" />。目前，它收藏在荷蘭[[阿姆斯特丹|阿姆斯特丹]]的[[梵高博物館|梵高博物館]]內<ref name="Guardian" />。

==歷史==
[[File:Van_Gogh_-_Felshügel_mit_Eiche.jpeg|thumb]]
梵高在完成《蒙馬儒的日落》後把畫轉折到其弟兼藝術品商人[[西奧·梵高_(商人)|西奧]]手中<ref name="VGmus">{{Cite web |url=http://www.vangoghmuseum.nl/vgm/index.jsp?page=330726&lang=en |title=Van Gogh Museum discovers new painting by Vincent van Gogh: Sunset at Montmajour |access-date=2013-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140429011709/http://www.vangoghmuseum.nl/vgm/index.jsp?page=330726&lang=en |archive-date=2014-04-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。其後，該畫作於1901年賣出<ref name=VGmus/>。1908年，一名[[挪威|挪威]]收藏家買入此畫，並藏在家中的閣樓中<ref name="BBC" />。1970年，收藏家離世，其家人在處理遺物時發現此畫，而令畫作重見天日<ref name=NPR>{{Cite web |url=http://www.npr.org/blogs/thetwo-way/2013/09/09/220625774/new-van-gogh-painting-identified-was-in-a-norwegian-attic |title='New' Van Gogh Painting Identified; Was In A Norwegian Attic |access-date=2013-09-11 |archive-date=2015-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150404055630/http://www.npr.org/blogs/thetwo-way/2013/09/09/220625774/new-van-gogh-painting-identified-was-in-a-norwegian-attic |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1991年，該畫已轉到他人之手，這名物主其後要求梵高博物館為畫作驗明正身，但由於這畫欠缺[[簽名|簽名]]而被認為並非出於梵高手筆<ref name="BBC" />。

隨著科技的進步和更多文獻被發掘，梵高博物館的專家用兩年時間終於鑑定《蒙馬儒的日落》為梵高的真迹。博物館館長Axel Ruger指此畫作零碎和強力的筆觸與梵高的畫功相似﹔其技巧也和《[[岩石_(梵高畫作)|岩石]]》相同﹔顏料與[[阿爾勒|阿爾勒]]畫室的調色盤上的一致；畫布是梵高所慣用的；畫背後「180」的數字，與西奧的收藏品編號脗合<ref name=NYT1>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/09/10/arts/design/new-van-gogh-painting-discovered-in-amsterdam.html?pagewanted=1&_r=0&adxnnl=1&adxnnlx=1378733687-TfBqJ4zhlBSFDSOo%2F0huDw |title=Museum Identifies New Van Gogh Painting in Amsterdam |access-date=2022-03-27 |archive-date=2018-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180108175448/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/09/10/arts/design/new-van-gogh-painting-discovered-in-amsterdam.html?pagewanted=1&_r=0&adxnnl=1&adxnnlx=1378733687-TfBqJ4zhlBSFDSOo%2F0huDw |dead-url=no }}</ref>。再加上梵高寫給西奧的信中提到：{{quote|昨天日落時，我在長有細小歪斜橡樹的崎嶇荒原。蒙馬儒這地方非常浪漫，實在沒有其它地方能比得上它，陽光傾瀉到灌木和地面上，一片金黃<ref name=NYT1/>。}}

在這些的證據下，館方最終於2013年9月9日對外宣佈證實《蒙馬儒的日落》這幅流傳於民間百年的油畫為梵高的真跡，並把它納入館藏中。

